name: TYMKRS: The Rabbit Hole
overview: TYMKRS: The White Rabbit is a homebrew NES game that was made as a Christmas present to the Tymkrs.  A second copy was made as a gift for the annual White Elephant gift exchange event for the hackerspace the Tymkrs hosts, "The Rabbit Hole". As a celebration of that hackerspace, the project utilized The Rabbit Hole name and logo.
